{"type": "article", "id": 59304, "title": "百度发布年终视频来“记住 2018”，微软上线了一款 Windows 95 毛衣 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-12-14T05:04:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5801, "name": "年终总结"}, {"id": 261, "name": "百度"}, {"id": 260, "name": "微软"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181214123539T0IPs6zYl4Fdr2Df.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4ODIyNzcxMA==&amp;mid=2651109687&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=3a022cbf1378664379edbcd229a5f09d&amp;chksm=8bdd7326bcaafa307cfac3cdfcfca4df665c333cbc7b10164affcf8486699e42f7a423807ff9&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=12131kEISsffkN4i6DlbTARu&amp;key=f27627979fcd26b3a9a0a61259fb6c422a63846b03fd31c1c43687ebd3c2c65ff6b900ef8a741af2b1f5fea621fba1f95689d97d77627792fb60adc681678abf3bc9515b7401c78b2c2880db9b32c0cc&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=k3SLyACq%2F9imcbSKmv%2BgtHsn4npzpNV1SISmkpZQKLoV9aLKXnRPeoph9619CplQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>喜茶和塔卡沙圣诞季联名合作。</b></a>既有联名圣诞杯套，还推出了联名圣诞福袋，包含围巾、包包、日历等联名限定，目前圣诞杯套已经在喜茶各门店上线，圣诞福袋还需消费者于平安夜在指定门店，通过喜茶的圣诞贺卡来获取。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812141236353wURD2lq6dPjnacB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501449\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181214123635v7KW4BDFc8CLjpgQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501449\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181214123637ZsCQxGVlzkch3qRM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181214123635oPFk1RWiV0KGIMDc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"Xinv\">“双 12” 期间，<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4316361318580975?\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>网易云音乐和知乎联合推出 RedBlue 联合笔记本，</b></a>选择了双方的各自代表色红蓝，并用一份“知音日报”详细介绍了此次合作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812141238144oH7xRLkpZcWiFOn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181214123814wSRDJTOuYVoApE5v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664828\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181214123814nGgRf1coWY7kVdPC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.324961\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的Case</h3><p line=\"VmxI\">今天是星巴克的天猫超级品牌日，<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjg4Mzg5ODA0MA==&amp;mid=2656250354&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=874eb89963b398f00ed306c0972beda1&amp;chksm=987cb425af0b3d33dbeb29d2be46caa8311d3ff09bfbaeb02fa0ae51297c19dd5bb45fbc7e52&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1214CSs2fFXmCEeq3zzr0t0o&amp;key=f00f0b2ae94b544518ab2295126b7cd5aafc0705d9b7a1890c0b1ef05436d386be26ac2a2b345d1f0d8699b76568dc80a7af9e827bf3b92dfd6e24d8f6c3f95c2172acdc58c3843f990241d18838e064&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=k3SLyACq%2F9imcbSKmv%2BgtHsn4npzpNV1SISmkpZQKLoV9aLKXnRPeoph9619CplQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>限定发售直通星级星礼卡，</b></a>有定制“直通玉星星礼卡”和“直通金星星礼卡”两款。还推出了圣诞礼盒，包括圣诞杯、星礼卡等，以及相框纪念徽章等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812141238493nbOvxGMu4p0RBaZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.364198\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"7lDS\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Windows/status/1073341012884500480\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Windows 官方推特今天正式发布了 Windows 95 毛衣。</b></a>这款“丑丑毛衣”（Ugly Sweater）饰以 Windows 95 的开机 Logo。微软使用 “Soft Wear” 来指代这款产品，读音一语双关。不过这款毛衣目前只能通过抽取幸运儿的方式获得。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812141239281rf9eIWCbFp0xSNy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812141239289TYjRZ3Uu718WcGk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181214123928AL40vWhtJHSxTlnw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"2RhE\">百度发布了年终盘点视频<b>“<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/2525235360/4316737929963977\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">记住 2018”</a></b>，回顾这一年中国人都在关注什么。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=z0809wr834d\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"0c21\">宝马 x GQ 高级职能研究所新一期探讨了<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4316796720764410?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“你，会开房吗？”</b></a>，如何在入住高级酒店不露怯的<b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/pym7u4Lv7tAXHAQU5Z2PoA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 16 个 Tips。</a></b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181214124257g0OLpKHANyaf3kt1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181214124235mDaxoIh7VNQeYndq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p>别克找来“奇葩说”里的金靖、赵英男、李思恒等人上演了<a href=\"https://car.weibo.com/pcview?alias=42745\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>“沙雕英雄传”</b></a>，通过搞怪的表演方式，来展现别克英朗的优势。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=g0812u2lykh\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p081249ym67\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=k0812prvjaq\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"mlMW\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3ODgwNTAzNw==&amp;mid=2659019444&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=baf33dc7555c1fc1127d6ca032ae8077&amp;chksm=8434ebf6b34362e0b68373c5b20ffc199e8a4cf1025df2b85b494a327d8052146a053253575c&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=12134oJFJ3BaWPUKQJ6GUbXg&amp;key=ea9727dab47f69a80d98428a0763db99d7dc60535762e4da4cf4cb81dc7bcf6895ce30bfe0228072c7a766ed57b9031c7cd65df856e41e88fc5a35cf370e302109f7603101fd6ffdab6f3f142c20160c&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=k3SLyACq%2F9imcbSKmv%2BgtHsn4npzpNV1SISmkpZQKLoV9aLKXnRPeoph9619CplQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>抖音推出“达人 P!CK 计划”，</b></a>鼓励达人自然有创意地植入广告信息。他们在收获广告收入同时，也能帮助账号涨粉，双方进行内容的长期合作。</p><p line=\"CWEw\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3ODgwNTAzNw==&amp;mid=2659019444&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=baf33dc7555c1fc1127d6ca032ae8077&amp;chksm=8434ebf6b34362e0b68373c5b20ffc199e8a4cf1025df2b85b494a327d8052146a053253575c&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=12134oJFJ3BaWPUKQJ6GUbXg&amp;key=ea9727dab47f69a80d98428a0763db99d7dc60535762e4da4cf4cb81dc7bcf6895ce30bfe0228072c7a766ed57b9031c7cd65df856e41e88fc5a35cf370e302109f7603101fd6ffdab6f3f142c20160c&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=k3SLyACq%2F9imcbSKmv%2BgtHsn4npzpNV1SISmkpZQKLoV9aLKXnRPeoph9619CplQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>广告主可在一条朋友圈广告添加多家门店信息，上限暂定为 100 家。</b></a>广告系统将智能拉取并向用户展示离他最近的门店，引导用户到店转化。</p><p line=\"qCds\">WPP集团 CEO Mark Read 最近在一封内部邮件中宣布，<a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/wpp-hires-away-longtime-publicis-vet-to-serve-as-first-chief-marketing-and-growth-officer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>将聘请前阳狮集团旗下的资深广告人 Laurent Ezekiel 为集团首个全球首席营销兼增长官，</b></a>并且直接向 Mark Read 汇报。</p><p line=\"qCds\" class=\"\">题图来自：Twitter<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Windows/status/1073341012884500480\" rel=\"nofollow\">@Windows</a></p>"}